Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Male' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
And I select 'Pelvis, whole soft part' radio button from Page 01 of Pelvic MRI
Then Page 04 of Pelvic MRI is activated

When I go to Page 04 of Pelvic MRI
Then 'Prostate Size' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Finding' tab is enabled

When I click on 'Finding' tab
Then 'Normal appearance of the prostate' radio button is enabled
And 'Finding' radio button is enabled

When I click on 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Residual hemorrhage' from 'Finding' dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse/flat' radio button is enabled

When I click on the localizer
And I click on 'TZ Base right anterior' zone
And I click on 'TZ Base right posterior' zone
Then 'TZ Base right anterior' zone is selected
And 'TZ Base right posterior' zone is selected
